snippet.title: AVENGERS: DOOMSDAY (2026) | Black Panther Trailer | Marvel Comics | Concept
snippet.description:
#Marvel #Avengers #Avengersdoomsday #ChrisEvans #Robertdowneyjr 
 
🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The Avengers: Doomsday Trailer teases an epic new chapter in the Marvel Cinematic Universe as Wakanda rises to face a world-ending threat in Avengers: Doomsday (2026). The Avengers Doomsday official trailer hints at the return of Robert Downey Jr. as Doctor Doom, setting up a powerful clash that reshapes the MCU and launches Marvel Phase 6. Packed with breathtaking action, comic-inspired visuals, and high-stakes drama, the Avengers Doomsday teaser trailer promises one of the most ambitious Marvel movies ever from Marvel Studios.

The inspiration behind this video:
The Avengers Doomsday trailer has finally dropped, and the road to Avengers 2026 officially begins now! In this video, we break down every explosive moment of the Avengers Doomsday official trailer, analyzing the destruction and the stakes for Earth's Mightiest Heroes. As Marvel Studios prepares for the biggest theatrical event of the year, we discuss how this Avengers Doomsday movie serves as the terrifying kickoff to Marvel Phase 6. Whether you are watching for the action or the lore, this breakdown of the Avengers Doomsday marvel trailer covers everything you need to know about the most anticipated Avengers Doomsday update yet.

The internet is still buzzing about the terrifying presence of Robert Downey Jr Doctor Doom. We dive deep into the massive Avengers Doomsday cast, debating whether this variant is a twisted version of Tony Stark or the true Victor Von Doom from the comics. This isn't just a team-up; the footage makes it look like a solo Doctor Doom movie where the villain finally wins. We analyze the Doctor Doom MCU suit upgrades and what the Avengers Doomsday teaser reveals about his war against the remaining Avengers. If you are here for the Robert Downey Jr MCU comeback, this video explores every theory regarding the Avengers Doctor Doom conflict.

Finally, we connect the dots between the lingering plot threads of MCU Phase 5 and the multiverse saga's climax in the Marvel Cinematic Universe. We hunt for easter eggs in the Dr Doom trailer footage and discuss how the doomsday trailer sets up the ultimate sacrifice. From the visual tone to the hidden cameos, we leave no stone unturned in this analysis. Don't miss our full reaction to the Avengers Doomsday trailer official release and our predictions for who survives the wrath of Marvel's greatest villain.

◖Made/Edited By Us◗
(SFX, VFX, Art) 
► Art by TeaserCon IG:  /teaserconofficial
◖Attention viewers◗ This Film & Animation video created only for Entertainment. 
Most of VFX created by us.

Thank You So Much For Watching!
Subscribe Now For More.

Your art made them. Now watch them come to life!
This film is a celebration of every sketch, every style, every fan-made legend 👑

Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale

Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Tower Troops from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

snippet.title: GIMS - OVERTON (Official Lyrics Vidéo)
snippet.description:
GIMS - OVERTON (Official Lyrics Vidéo)
OVERTON disponible en streaming : https://gims.bfan.link/overton
Abonne-toi à la chaîne : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCB1Byx5yTbLpQaV-rlfmtA

TikTok : https://www.tiktok.com/@gims_off
Instagram :https://www.instagram.com/gims/
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/gims
Twitter : https://twitter.com/GIMS/
Snapchat : Warano75

Paroles :
On va les scier pendant qu'ils dorment
J'suis né loin d'ici genre à 200 000 bornes
Cligne des yeux, j'fais passer 40 tonnes
J'suis à la fenêtre à côté d'Overton
On redoute plus rien car le pire est fait
Donc on attend l'oseille de pieds fermes
Remercie très peu pour les bienfaits
Message crypté sur le billet vert
Tout plein de regrets comme un apôtre
J'arrive tête baissée sous les applause
Tout en surveillant le ciel comme à Naplouse
Pendant qu'ils guettent ma métamorphose
Plus de bastos qu'Oliver Kahn
Petit dej Martinez, bref j'suis à Cannes
J'arrive en dansant parce que j'ai un plan
J'arrive péssa comme Bioman blanc
Tu vis, tu meurs, c'est le contrat
Rafale de plomb sur le flanc droit
On prie tous sans savoir qui est sous le drap
Foyer, bresom Sonacotra 
Ne cherche pas à bronzer sous le ciel gris
Celui qui demande, c'est celui qui a fait le crime
Peu importe la science que tu décryptes
Ça se passera comme dans les écrits
C'est le buteur qui récolte les mérites
C’est plus des couplets que j'écris, c'est des rites
Toc-toc-toc devant la porte, c'est Derrick
Dans la tête, j'ai des formules, j'ai des RIB
Le banquier lit l'avenir dans un sac de blé
Tout était écrit comme à l'Urssaf
Le MIB va venir m'aveugler
J'ai le cœur vide et la maison meublée
Les points serrés, seul, debout sur une gargouille
Effusion Kill Bill, j'me débarbouille
La mort travaille sans aucun stress
Expédition vers La Paintresse
Cette nuit, l'ennemi m'a sous-estimé
Cette flèche dans l'arbre m'était destinée
Chaque cicatrice m'a inspiré
Inconsciemment comme respirer
Faire confiance, j'ai testé, c'est horrible
Tu vas m'trahir selon mes théories
J'manie la plume comme une épée maudite
Amorti d'la poitrine dans la météorite
J'suis distrait pendant nos échanges
Les murs chuchotent des langues étranges
La vie m'secoue mais je reste droit
Comme la surface du liquide quand le verre penche
Rafiot visible depuis les quais
Je sors un single il neige durant l'été
Le cœur forgé d'un métal épais
Devise familiale en tirant l'épée
Ils veulent nous tatouer le code barre
Leur livre de chevet c'est le code noir
Pas de prisonnier, c'est pas rentable
L’ennemi supplie, c'est lamentable
J'me balade à Midgard avec mon fils
La tête d'Ymir à la ceinture
Les larmes se mêlent à la peinture
J’suis Killer Bee sans la teinture
Ils ont plus de mana, plus de potions
Dialecte ancien, j'ai des notions
À la SACEM, j'traîne en chaussons
Dette colonial, c'est la caution

#GIMS #OVERTON

snippet.title: George Michael - Careless Whisper (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
#carelesswhisper #georgemichael #lyrics #S&R #tiktok #viral 
George Michael - Careless Whisper (Lyrics)

[Intro]
Time can never mend
The careless whispers
Of a good friend
To the heart and mind
Ignorance is kind
There's no comfort in the truth
Pain is all you'll find
Should've known better, yeah

[Instrumental]

[Verse 1]
I feel so unsure
As I take your hand
And lead you to the dance floor
As the music dies
Something in your eyes
Calls to mind a silver screen
And all its sad goodbyes

[Chorus]
I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
Should've known better than to cheat a friend
And waste a chance that I've been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Verse 2]
Time can never mend
The careless whispers
Of a good friend
To the heart and mind
Ignorance is kind
There's no comfort in the truth
Pain is all you'll find

[Chorus]
I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
Should've known better than to cheat a friend
(Should've known better, yeah)
And waste a chance that I've been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Post-Chorus]
Never without your love

[Bridge]
Tonight, the music seems so loud
I wish that we could lose this crowd
Maybe it's better this way
We'd hurt each other with the things we want to say
We could have been so good together
We could have lived this dance forever
But now, who's gonna dance with me?
Please stay

[Chorus]
And I'm never gonna dance again
Guilty feet have got no rhythm
Though it's easy to pretend
I know you're not a fool
Should've known better than to cheat a friend
And waste a chance that I've been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

[Outro]
(Now that you're gone)
Now that you're gone
(Now that you're gone)
Was what I did so wrong, so wrong
That you had to leave me alone?

snippet.description:
Aujourd'hui, j'ai Triché contre mon pote dans un combat de mob minecraft, mais tout est au hasard (enfin sauf pour moi muahahhaha)
Mail pour tout contact commercial : azpaztv@gmail.com
Mon Twitter : https://www.twitter.com/azpaztv
Mon Discord  + de nulcraft : https://discord.gg/EBPCS6YF9e
Merci pour les 700k road to 800k
Ce n'est pas Minecraft, Mais l'eau monte ou Minecraft, mais la lave monte, ou Survivre 100 jours dans Minecraft, ou tout type de défi dans Minecraft mais. Il s'agit d'un speedrun / Manhunt . Shorts ou sur Roblox avec des Brainrot Italien de Steal a brainrot grow a garden ou 99 nuits en forêt c'est des jeux de fou surtout vole un brainrot roblox fr
Dans cette vidéo Minecraft 1.20 (1.21 et non 1.19, 1.18 ou 1.17), je répondrai à toutes les questions que vous me poserez sans faire une seule exception. Il y a des questions embarrassantes, des questions intéressantes et beaucoup d'entre elles tout simplement stupides XD Cette vidéo est l'une de mes préférées que j'ai faites, alors profitez-en :)

Ce n'est pas Minecraft dans la vraie vie, pas l'édition éducative de Minecraft, pas Minecraft, mais en difficulté millionaire de riche. ou alors 7 façons de voler mes amis Cela répond à vos questions les plus litigieuses/absurdes.

Je vous aime tous beaucoup!
